OL,4,CCovid vaccine: Fasting during Ramadan
OL,5,C'should not stop Muslims getting jab'
OL,6, Islamic scholars and NHS leaders are
OL,7, urging Muslims not to let fasting over
OL,8, Ramadan stop them getting a Covid jab.
OL,10,FDuring Ramadan many Muslims abstain
OL,11,Ffrom food and drink in daylight hours.
OL,13,FIslamic teaching says Muslims should
OL,14,Frefrain "from anything entering the
OL,15,Fbody" between sunrise and sunset.
OL,17,FBut Qari Asim, an imam in Leeds, said
OL,18,Fthat because the vaccine goes into the
OL,19,Fmuscle rather than the bloodstream and
OL,20,Fis not nutritious, it does not amount
OL,21,Fto breaking the fast.
